License Number.instruction: The unique identifier number for the driver's license

Date of Birth.instruction: The date of birth of the license holder

Issue Date.instruction: The date the driver's license was issued

Expiration Date.instruction: The date the driver's license expires

Name.instruction: The full name of the license holder

Address.instruction: The residential address of the license holder

License Class.instruction: The class of driver's license held by the license holder

State.instruction: The state that issued the driver's license

Organ Donor.instruction: Indicates if the license holder is an organ donor

Restrictions.instruction: Any restrictions on the driver's license

Sex.instruction: The sex of the license holder

Height.instruction: The height of the license holder

Eye Color.instruction: The eye color of the license holder

Charge.instruction: The charge amount for the driver's license
